h1= title
h3 Here's the Posts
p 
  a(href='/post/create') Add Post
p Oh right, here they are:
table.posts
  tr
    th Title
    th Category
    th User
    th Created
  - each post in posts
    - date = new Date(post.created_at)
    - postDate= date.toDateString()
    tr
      td
        a(href='/post/#{post._id}') #{post.title} \n
      td= post.category
      td= post.user_id
      td= postDate

